	<header class="pb-8 md:pb-24">
		<div class="container mx-auto px-10 pt-20 md:pt-24 pb-24 text-center md:text-left">
			<img class="inline" src="/assets/img/splash-logo.svg"alt="rainersimon.io">
			<p class="text-white md:text-xl pt-1 md:pb-8">Web Development / Maps / UI / Open Source</p>
		</div>
	</header>

	<main>
		<section class="container mx-auto px-10 pt-12 pb-24 md:pt-20 text-gray-800 text-lg">
			<div class="max-w-screen-md">
				<p class="font-bold pb-10 text-xl">
					Hi, I'm Rainer. I create software for people working with data.
				</p>
					
				<p class="pb-10">
					I specialize in the design of tools that help people explore, 
					analyze and manage data more easily. I am passionate about maps, 
					and in many of my projects, I have dealt with spatial or cartographic data.  
				</p>

				<p class="pb-12">
					I am also the maintainer of the <a href="https://annotorious.dev">Annotorious</a> and
					<a href="https://github.com/recogito/text-annotator-js">Recogito Text Annotator</a> open source 
					libraries for image and text annotation, and the former lead developer of the award-winning and 
					<a href="https://what-is-dh-the-album.netlify.app/singles/recogito/">song-inspiring</a>&nbsp;<a href="https://recogito.pelagios.org">Recogito</a> annotation platform.
				</p>

				<a 
					class="btn inline-flex items-center h-10 px-6 text-md transition-colors duration-150 rounded-md focus:shadow-outline text-white bg-steel-light hover:bg-steel-lighter" 
